s?<br /> </strong>Spontaneous Broadway and Theatresports -- singing and silliness.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Best moment on the BATS stage?<br /> </strong>Getting married to Paul Killam in an opera about giants and gay marriage. It was the perfect combination of ridiculousness and sincerity.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why should people study improv?<br /> </strong>Once you realize that your entire life is improvised, you can apply the same skills that let you carry off a stage performance with aplomb to just about any situation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Any improv advice?<br /> </strong>Look to your partner! He or she knows everything you need to make the scene fabulous.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are your artistic influences?<br /> </strong>I can only aspire to be as theatrical as Prince, as exciting as <em>Die Hard,</em> and as hummable as <em>Avenue Q</em>.</p>'),(2653,335,'_right_column','field_52f276e1f1ba0'),(2654,217,'extra_image_1','1677'),(2655,217,'_extra_image_1','field_52f273e29b5db'),(2656,217,'extra_image_2','1678'),(2657,217,'_extra_image_2','field_52f27616cf901'),(2658,217,'extra_image_3','1679'),(2659,217,'_extra_image_3','field_52f27626cf902'),(2660,217,'right_column','<h1>Q &amp; A</h1>\r\n<p><strong>What was your first BATS show?<br /></strong>1987 with the Bolognas, Brian Lohmann, Greg Proops, and Rafe Chase in San Francisco</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are your favorite formats?<br /></strong>Improvised Tarantino, True Fiction Magazine (stories inside of stories), one-act and three-act improvised plays</p>\r\n<p><strong>Funniest moment on the BATS stage?<br /></strong>In a Theatresports™ match, the other team had to do a scene in the time it took Ed Alter and me to exchange clothes.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are your artistic influences?<br /></strong>John Steinbeck, Jean Shelton, Warner Brothers cartoons</p>\r\n<p><strong>Favorite movie?<br /></strong>There are many I love, but the one that changed my life was <em>Some Like It Hot.</em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Favorite play?<br /></strong><em>A Streetcar Named Desire</em></p>'),(2661,217,'_right_column','field_52f276e1f1ba0'),(2662,345,'_edit_lock','1401246197:2'),(2663,345,'_edit_last','2'),(2664,345,'_content_block_information',''),(2665,348,'_edit_lock','1446375651:4'),(2666,348,'_edit_last','4'),(2667,348,'_wp_page_template','otg-page.php'),(2668,348,'_responsive_layout','default'),(2669,349,'_edit_lock','1446374981:4'),(2670,349,'_edit_last','4'),(2671,349,'_wp_page_template','otg-page.php'),(2672,349,'_responsive_layout','default'),(2673,350,'_edit_last','2'),(2674,350,'_edit_lock','1401575856:2'),(2675,350,'_wp_page_template','otg-page.php'),(2676,350,'_responsive_layout','default'),(2677,351,'_edit_last','2'),(2678,351,'_edit_lock','1418779594:7'),(2679,351,'_wp_page_template','otg-page.php'),(2680,351,'_responsive_layout','default'),(2681,352,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2682,352,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2683,352,'_menu_item_object_id','351'),(2684,352,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2685,352,'_menu_item_target',''),(2686,352,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2687,352,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2688,352,'_menu_item_url',''),(2690,353,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2691,353,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2692,353,'_menu_item_object_id','350'),(2693,353,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2694,353,'_menu_item_target',''),(2695,353,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2696,353,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2697,353,'_menu_item_url',''),(2699,354,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2700,354,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2701,354,'_menu_item_object_id','349'),(2702,354,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2703,354,'_menu_item_target',''),(2704,354,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2705,354,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2706,354,'_menu_item_url',''),(2708,355,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2709,355,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2710,355,'_menu_item_object_id','348'),(2711,355,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2712,355,'_menu_item_target',''),(2713,355,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{