o be funny. <a title=\"About Improvised Theatre\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/about-improvised-theatre/\">Our style of improv</a> is all about listening, positivity, spontaneity, generosity, and genuine creativity -- and these are all skills that can be nurtured and developed. <a title=\"Foundation 1\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/foundation-1/\">Foundation 1</a> will introduce you to these basic improv skills and more.</p>'),(3587,408,'_faq_1_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3588,408,'faq','13'),(3589,408,'_faq','field_53739e36e08ea'),(3591,408,'faq_2_question','I\'m shy. I\'m not an \'actor type.\' I get stage fright. I\'ve done improv before and felt picked on. Why should I study improv at BATS?'),(3592,408,'_faq_2_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3593,408,'faq_2_answer','<p>Glad you asked! <a title=\"Why Study Improv at BATS\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/why-study-improv-at-bats/\">Here\'s why.</a></p>'),(3594,408,'_faq_2_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3595,408,'faq_3_question','What class should I start with? '),(3596,408,'_faq_3_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3597,408,'faq_3_answer','<p><a title=\"Foundation 1\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/foundation-1/\">Foundation 1</a>. Not sure you’re ready to commit to a six-week class? We also offer one-time, 3-hour <a title=\"3-hour Intro Workshops\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/3-hour-intro-workshops/\">Intro to Improv </a>and<a title=\"3-hour Intro Workshops\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/3-hour-intro-workshops/\"> Improv for Shy People</a> workshops.</p>'),(3598,408,'_faq_3_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3601,476,'_edit_lock','1419761804:4'),(3602,476,'_edit_last','4'),(3603,476,'show_type','shortform'),(3604,476,'_show_type','field_528677f80a6d3'),(3605,476,'day','friday'),(3606,476,'_day','field_52cc78fa2dd0e'),(3607,476,'team_1','TBA'),(3608,476,'_team_1','field_52cc8b4af0d87'),(3609,476,'team_2','TBA'),(3610,476,'_team_2','field_52cc8ccbf0d88'),(3