ield_53739e65e08eb'),(3871,110,'faq_0_answer','<p>Friday and Saturday <a title=\"Company Members\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/company-members/\">Main Stage Company</a> shows always start at 8 PM. Sunday <a title=\"Student Shows\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/student-shows/\">student shows</a> generally begin at 7 PM, but times can vary. Check the student shows schedule (at the bottom of the <a title=\"Student Shows\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/student-shows/\">student shows</a> page) for showtimes on specific dates.</p>'),(3872,110,'_faq_0_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3873,110,'faq_1_question','How long does the show last?'),(3874,110,'_faq_1_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3875,110,'faq_1_answer','<p>Friday and Saturday <a title=\"Company Members\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/company-members/\">Main Stage Company</a> shows generally run from 1 hour and 30 minutes to 1 hour and 45 minutes, including the 10-minute intermission. Sunday <a title=\"Student Shows\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/student-shows/\">student shows</a> run about 1 hour and 30 minutes. Because every show is completely improvised, the exact runtime of each show will vary.</p>'),(3876,110,'_faq_1_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3877,110,'faq_2_question','Do you serve alcohol or food?'),(3878,110,'_faq_2_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3879,110,'faq_2_answer','<p>Yes, we serve beer and wine (no drink minimum!) plus coffee, sodas, candy, cookies, and other tasty snacks. The BATS Café is open before the show and during intermission and is staffed by our friendly volunteers. All proceeds help support our nonprofit theatre company. Please note that we do not have a full bar and we do not offer full meals. We can, however, recommend some great <a title=\"Map &amp; Directions\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/about-us/map-directions/#restaurants\">restaurants nearby</a>.</p>'),(3880,110,'_faq_2_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3881,110,'faq_3_question','Is there reserved seating?'),(3882,110,'_faq_3_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3883,110,'faq_3_answer','<p>There is no reserved seating. All seating, including advance purchased tickets, is general admission. Our box office and the BATS Café open at 7:30, or 30 minutes prior to showtime on Sundays. We recommend arriving by 7:45 for your choice of seats. (<em>Hint:</em> the first and second rows have the most leg room!)</p><p>Have a group? We do offer reserved seating for groups of 10 or more. See <a title=\"Group Sales\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/group-sales/\">Group Sales </a>for details.</p>'),(3884,110,'_faq_3_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3885,110,'faq_4_question','Do I have to buy tickets in advance?'),(3886,110,'_faq_4_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3887,110,'faq_4_answer','<p>Although you don’t <em>have to</em> buy tickets in advance, we highly recommend it. Buying advance tickets is a great choice because it guarantees you a seat at the show <em>and</em> your ticket price is discounted from the door price. Our most popular shows — tournament semifinals and finals, holiday shows, and SF vs. LA shows — regularly sell out. We’re all about taking risks, but why risk missing a sold-out show?</p>'),(3888,110,'_faq_4_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3889,110,'faq_5_question','How do I buy tickets in advance?'),(3890,110,'_faq_5_question','field_53739e65e08eb'),(3891,110,'faq_5_answer','<p><a href=\"https://www.vendini.com/ticket-software.html?t=tix&amp;w=30f488d21474d07590852179c032e191\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> OR click the BUY TICKETS button at the top right of this page OR go to the <a title=\"Shows\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/shows/\">show schedule</a>, find the show you’re interested in, and click BUY TICKETS.</p><p>If you prefer to buy tickets at the door, the Bayfront Theater box office opens 30 minutes before show time (that means 7:30 PM for Friday and Saturday shows). Please note that the box office and BATS Café accept cash or check only (for now -- we’re working on it).</p>'),(3892,110,'_faq_5_answer','field_53739e8ce08ec'),(3893,110,'faq','18'),(3894,110,'_faq','field_53739e36e08ea'),(3895,489,'_wp_attached_file','2013/12/about-it.jpg'),(3896,489,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:215;s:6:\"height\";i:323;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2013/12/about-it.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"about-it-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"about-it-199x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:199;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(3897,490,'_wp_attached_file','2013/12/about-it2.jpg'),(3898,490,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:215;s:6:\"height\";i:159;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2013/12/about-it2.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"about-it2-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(3899,492,'_wp_attached_file','2013/12/group1.jpg'),(3900,492,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:332;s:6:\"height\";i:236;s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"2013/12/group1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"group1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"group1-300x213.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:213