up comedian, Paul has played the Improv in Hollywood, and in the UK he performed regularly at the Comedy Store, the Improv, the Jongleurs chain, as well as touring in Europe and on radio and TV. His show “How to be the Perfect Couple” was a hit at the Edinburgh Festival, and had a sell out run in the US.</p>'),(16537,1232,'_right_column','field_52f276e1f1ba0'),(16538,1233,'_wp_attached_file','2014/08/paul-rogan.jpg'),(16539,1233,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:236;s:6:\"height\";i:236;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2014/08/paul-rogan.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"paul-rogan-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(16540,1232,'_thumbnail_id','1233'),(16541,1234,'_wp_attached_file','2014/08/impro.jpg'),(16542,1234,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:192;s:6:\"height\";i:113;s:4:\"file\";s:17:\"2014/08/impro.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:17:\"impro-150x113.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:113;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(16543,1235,'_edit_lock','1437682574:7'),(16544,1235,'_edit_last','7'),(16545,1236,'_wp_attached_file','2014/08/floyd-vanbuskirk.jpg'),(16546,1236,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:236;s:6:\"height\";i:236;s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"2014/08/floyd-vanbuskirk.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"floyd-vanbuskirk-150x