sidebar','field_5380e7f58e3e8'),(22333,1684,'right_column','<h1>Q &amp; A</h1>\r\n<p><strong>What was your first BATS show?</strong><br /> I was in the audience for the  first public performance by BATS, November 10, 1986, at the New Conservatory Theater.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are your favorite formats?</strong><br /> Musicals, genre longforms</p>\r\n<p><strong>Best moment on the BATS stage?</strong><br /> So many…</p>\r\n<p><strong>Any improv advice?</strong><br /> Slow down and trust your instincts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are your artistic Influences?</strong><br /> Carol Burnett, Jonathan Winters, Gilda Radner, the Beatles, Major League Baseball (which taught me patience), and my parents.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Favorite movies?</strong><br /> Shawshank Redemption, Moonrise Kingdom, Singin’ in the Rain, West Side Story</p>\r\n<p><strong>Favorite music?</strong><br /> Beatles, classical, R&amp;B</p>\r\n<p><strong>Favorite live theatre? </strong><br /> Big-ass musicals</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why should people study improv?</strong><br /> Going from a “no” person to a “yes” person will change your life. Promise.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(22334,1684,'_right_column','field_52f276e1f1ba0'),(22335,1686,'_edit_lock','1431376729:5'),(22336,1686,'_edit_last','5'),(22337,1686,'class_type','f1'),(22338,1686,'_class_type','field_534c5961f4792'),(22339,1686,'start_date','20150526'),(22340,1686,'_start_date','field_534c5aef8c631'),(22341,1686,'end_date','20150526'),(22342,1686,'_end_date','field_534c5b2e8c632'),(22343,1686,'coach_label','Coach'),(22344,1686,'_coach_label','field_534c5a2ac5656'),(22345,1686,'coach','a:1:{i:0;s:3:\"225\";}'),(22346,1686,'_coach','field_534c5a74d202e'),(22347,1686,'sign_up_link','https://bats15052141.eventbrite.com'),(22348,1686,'_sign_up_link','field_534c5b9853ab5'),(22349,1686,'sidebar_text','<p>with John Remak<br />Tuesdays, 7:00–10:00 PM<br />May 26 – June 30, 2015<strong><br /> Cubberley Community Center, Palo Alto<br /> </strong></p>'),(22350,1686,'_si