=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"115\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Take a Class</h3>\r\n<p>Improv skills are life skills. Explore your inherent creativity in a fun, safe, and supportive environment. New classes start every week!</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"School of Improv\" href=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/school/\">Take a Class »</a></p>','Take a Class','','publish','closed','closed','','262','','','2014-12-04 16:54:46','2014-12-05 00:54:46','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=content_block&#038;p=262',0,'content_block','',0),(263,2,'2014-03-07 09:36:49','2014-03-07 16:36:49','<p><a href=\"http://www.improv.org/onthego/\"><img src=\"http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/bring-to-work.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"115\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Improv @ Work</h3>\r\n<p>Improve team effectiveness, unlock creativity, and build morale with customized trainings and performances from BATS Improv.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"BATS On-the-Go\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/onthego/\">Do Improv @ Work »</a></p>','Improv @ Work','','publish','closed','closed','','bring-us-to-work','','','2015-11-01 03:16:30','2015-11-01 11:16:30','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=content_block&#038;p=263',0,'content_block','',0),(264,2,'2014-03-07 09:43:50','2014-03-07 16:43:50','<p>Welcome to BATS Improv, Center for Improvised Theatre, the most highly acclaimed and longest-running improv company and school in San Francisco. <br /><br /> Feed your imagination. Be surprised. Bust a gut. Share in the delight of creation as completely improvised stories unfold before your eyes. <br /><br /> <a href=\"about-us\"> More about BATS Improv » </a> <br /><br /> <a href=\"shows\"> <img alt=\"\" src=\"wp-content/themes/responsive/core/images/show-schedule-button.png\" /> </a></p>','Welcome to BATS Improv','','publish','closed','closed','','welcome-to-bats-improv','','','2014-03-07 09:43:51','2014-03-07 16:43:51','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=content_block&#038;p=264',0,'content_block','',0),(266