m/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Kasey-Klemm_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(525,3,'2014-05-21 17:26:58','2014-05-22 00:26:58','Show up. In every sense of that phrase. Show up all the time. As much as you can. As best as you can.\r\n','Rebecca Poretsky, company member','','publish','open','open','','rebecca-poretsky-company-member','','','2014-05-23 11:00:19','2014-05-23 18:00:19','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=525',65,'quotes','',0),(526,3,'2014-05-21 17:26:47','2014-05-22 00:26:47','','Rebecca-Poretsky_92x92','','inherit','open','open','','rebecca-poretsky_92x92','','','2014-05-21 17:26:47','2014-05-22 00:26:47','',525,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Rebecca-Poretsky_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(527,3,'2014-05-21 17:28:26','2014-05-22 00:28:26','Take classes, perform, start a group, enjoy life, eat out more often.','John Remak, company member','','publish','open','open','','john-remak-company-member','','','2014-05-23 11:00:09','2014-05-23 18:00:09','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=527',64,'quotes','',0),(528,3,'2014-05-21 17:28:15','2014-05-22 00:28:15','','John-Remak_92x92','','inherit','open','open','','john-remak_92x92','','','2014-05-21 17:28:15','2014-05-22 00:28:15','',527,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/John-Remak_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(529,3,'2014-05-21 17:29:42','2014-05-22 00:29:42','Keep saying yes, and make your partner look good!','Jenny Rosen, company member','','publish','open','open','','jenny-rosen-company-member','','','2014-05-23 10:59:37','2014-05-23 17:59:37','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=529',63,'quotes','',0),(530,3,'2014-05-21 17:29:34','2014-05-22 00:29:34','','Jenny-Rosen_92x92','','inherit','open','open','','jenny-rosen_92x92','','','2014-05-21 17:29:34','2014-05-22 00:29:34','',529,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Jenny-Rosen_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(531,3,'2014-05-21 17:31:13','2014-05-22 00:31:13','Don\'t wait until you\'re a confident improviser to act like a confident improviser. Be changed.','Lisa Rowland, company member','','publish','open','open','','lisa-rowland-company-member','','','2014-05-23 10:59:32','2014-05-23 17:59:32','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=531',62,'quotes','',0),(532,3,'2014-05-21 17:30:56','2014-05-22 00:30:56','','Lisa-Rowland_92x92','','inherit','open','open','','lisa-rowland_92x92','','','2014-05-21 17:30:56','2014-05-22 00:30:56','',531,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Lisa-Rowland_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(533,3,'2014-05-21 17:34:01','2014-05-22 00:34:01','Slow down and trust your instincts.','Barbara Scott, company member','','publish','open','open','','barbara-scott-company-member','','','2014-05-23 10:59:26','2014-05-23 17:59:26','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=533',61,'quotes','',0),(534,3,'2014-05-21 17:33:47','2014-05-22 00:33:47','','Barbara-Scott_92x92','','inherit','open','open','','barbara-scott_92x92','','','2014-05-21 17:33:47','2014-05-22 00:33:47','',533,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Barbara-Scott_92x92.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(535,2,'2014-05-21 18:57:51','2014-05-22 01:57:51','<div class=\"gift-certificate\"><h2><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536\" src=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/six-pack.jpg\" alt=\"six-pack\" width=\"127\" height=\"134\" />Show Six-Pack - $90</h2><p>Gift yourself or a friend with six tickets to BATS. Come to six shows on your own, or bring a friend to three, or treat two-thirds of the Supreme Court to one, or (you get the picture.)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.eventbrite.com/e/bats-improv-show-six-pack-tickets-3601715829\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-537 size-full\" src=\"http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/purchase.png\" alt=\"purchase