','','2014-05-23 20:38:03','2014-05-24 03:38:03','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=624',38,'quotes','',0),(625,3,'2014-05-23 20:18:21','2014-05-24 03:18:21','<p>“A benchmark for improv all over the world”</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>– </em><em>Bay Area Critic</em></p>','Bay Area Critic','','publish','open','open','','bay-area-critic-2','','','2014-05-23 20:38:25','2014-05-24 03:38:25','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=625',39,'quotes','',0),(626,3,'2014-05-23 20:19:16','2014-05-24 03:19:16','<p class=\"Body1\">One of “20 Best Improv Comedy Schools Around the World”</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>–</em> <em>Rant Lifestyle</em></p>','Rant Lifestyle','','publish','open','open','','rant-lifestyle','','','2014-05-23 20:38:48','2014-05-24 03:38:48','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=626',40,'quotes','',0),(627,3,'2014-05-23 20:20:36','2014-05-24 03:20:36','<p>“Their exercises brought us together in ways we had not experienced before.”</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>– Dr. Scott Abramson, Kaiser Permanente </em></p>','Dr. Scott Abramson, Kaiser Permanente','','publish','open','open','','dr-scott-abramson-kaiser-permanente','','','2014-05-23 20:20:36','2014-05-24 03:20:36','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=627',29,'quotes','',0),(628,3,'2014-05-23 20:37:34','2014-05-24 03:37:34','<p class=\"Body1\">“I love the playful, can\'t fail, theatrical nature of BATS\'s philosophy.”</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>– BATS Student</em></p>','BATS Student 8','','publish','open','open','','bats-student-8','','','2014-05-23 20:37:34','2014-05-24 03:37:34','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=quotes&#038;p=628',36,'quotes','',0),(629,4,'2014-05-23 21:37:15','2014-05-24 04:37:15','<p>A cast of four talented improvisers and one musician spontaneously and simultaneously create two distinct \"films,\" each unique in genre, tone, and character, and each inspired by an original title supplied by the audience.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to presenting two great, fully improvised stories, Double Feature™ adds fun and excitement as the improvisers must play multiple characters (often in the same scene) as they bounce back and forth between two stories. Created by Company Member Rafe Chase, Double Feature, is one of BATS most popular shows.</p>\r\n<p>VIDEOS:<br /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EiaiJnDUD8I\" target=\"_blank\">Character Switching in Double Feature</a><br /> <a href=\"http://youtu.be/OGGZQBORjtc\" target=\"_blank\">Rafe Chase on Double Feature</a></p>','Double Feature™','','draft','open','open','','double-feature','','','2015-08-20 21:00:23','2015-08-21 04:00:23','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=saturday&#038;p=629',10,'saturday','',0),(630,4,'2014-05-23 21:15:55','2014-05-24 04:15:55','','double-feature-web313','','inherit','open','open','','double-feature-web313','','','2014-05-23 21:15:55','2014-05-24 04:15:55','',629,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/double-feature-web313.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(631,4,'2014-05-23 21:42:15','2014-05-24 04:42:15','','la-battle-web315','','inherit','open','open','','la-battle-web315','','','2014-05-23 21:42:15','2014-05-24 04:42:15','',476,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/la-battle-web315.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(633,4,'2014-05-23 21:47:01','2014-05-24 04:47:01','<p>Travel back in time with us to 1959, when a ground breaking, mind bending new television show appeared that shattered changed everything. Each night we’ll create four brand new, completely improvised, never before seen and never-to-be-seen again episodes of the iconic show, taking you into the fifth dimension.  Into the middle ground between light and shadow, between science and superstition, into the pit between our fears and the summit of our knowledge.  We invite you to join us in the dimension of imagination and offer YOUR suggestions to rocket us into the Improvised Twilight Zone!</p>','Improvised Twilight Zone','','draft','open','open','','twilightzone','','','2015-08-20 12:41:51','2015-08-20 19:41:51','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=friday&#038;p=633',10,'friday','',0),(634,4,'2014-05-23 22:01:09','2014-05-24 05:01:09','<p>These are the voyages of a Starship to be named by you, the audience! Its mission: to explore new characters, to seek out new dangerous and intense relationships, and to boldly go where no improv has gone before!</p>\r\n<p>Warp Speed is a completely improvised salute to that classic sci-fi TV series of the 60s. Instead seeing Kirk and Spock (or spoofs of Kirk and Spock), your suggestions will beam aboard an all-new crew of characters, created and introduced on the spot!</p>\r\n<p>Like every show at BATS, nothing will have been pre-planned or discussed in advance. There are no “stock characters” or pre-determined plot points or situations. Everything from the plot, to the dialogue, to the characters, to the music — and even the lighting cues — will be made up on the spot!</p>','Warp Speed<br><i>An Improvised Trek</i>','','draft','open','open','','warp-speed-july','','','2015-08-20 21:00:18','2015-08-21 04:00:18','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=saturday&#038;p=634',9,'saturday','',0),(639,4,'2014-05-24 00:23:47','2014-05-24 07:23:47','','nye-web315','','inherit','open','open','','nye-web315','','','2014-05-24 00:23:47','2014-05-24 07:23:47','',83,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/nye-web315.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(640,4,'2014-05-24 00:59:13','2014-05-24 07:59:13','','holiday-musical-web315','','inherit','open','open','','holiday-musical-web315','','','2014-05-24 00:59:13','2014-05-24 07:59:13','',81,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/holiday-musical-web315.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(641,4,'2014-05-24 01:02:27','2014-05-24 08:02:27','','nye-web315','','inherit','open','open','','nye-web315-2','','','2014-05-24 01:02:27','2014-05-24 08:02:27','',83,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/nye-web3151.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(642,4,'2014-05-24 01:04:59','2014-05-24 08:04:59','','holiday-musical-web315','','inherit','open','open','','holiday-musical-web315-2','','','2014-05-24 01:04:59','2014-05-24 08:04:59','',81,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/holiday-musical-web3151.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(644,4,'2014-05-24 06:24:56','2014-05-24 13:24:56','','holiday-musical-web315','','inherit','open','open','','holiday-musical-web315-3','','','2014-05-24 06:24:56','2014-05-24 13:24:56','',81,'http://bats.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/holiday-musical-web3152.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(645,4,'2014-05-24 06:40:05','2014-05-24 13:40:05','<p>One of our most popular shows returns for the holidays! Set in England in the 1930\'s, a group of delightfully eccentric characters gathers at a manor to celebrate the season. But they soon find out that someone\'s been very naughty indeed.  Witness the murder, then follow the detective as they uncover clues, and search for the killer. Because it\'s improvised, no one, not even the actors, will know whodunit until the shocking finale!</p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"color: #d9541e;\"><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Group Tickets\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/groups/\"><strong>Group tickets</strong> start at just $14 each!</a><br /><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\">You can also give this show as a gift with a </a><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\"><strong>BATS Gift Certific</strong><strong>ate</strong>.</a> <strong><br /></strong></span></em></p>','Merry Murder Mystery','','draft','open','open','','merrymurdermystery','','','2015-06-22 13:20:16','2015-06-22 20:20:16','',0,'http://bats.wpengine.com/?post_type=special