 show is unique and always full of hilarious surprises; you can expect lots of variety and audience participation.</p>\r\n<p>For this tournament, the BATS Main Stage Company has split into six teams, each team competing for the honor to represent San Francisco in the <a href=\"http://www.improv.org/special/annual-grudge-match/\">SF vs. LA Grudge Match</a> in August. Every Friday in June and July, two teams will face off by performing a variety of scenes, games, and even musical numbers — all completely improvised and all inspired by your suggestions!</p>\r\n<p>The team with the most points at the end of the match is declared the winner and moves one step closer to the <strong>Championship Match on July 25</strong>.</p>','Theatresports&trade;','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-22 21:30:02','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=sport&p=1550',2,'sport','',0),(1553,7,'2014-12-26 12:16:09','2014-12-26 20:16:09','','kimberly1','','inherit','open','open','','kimberly1','','','2014-12-26 12:16:09','2014-12-26 20:16:09','',222,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/kimberly1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1554,7,'2014-12-26 12:16:11','2014-12-26 20:16:11','','kimberly2','','inherit','open','open','','kimberly2','','','2014-12-26 12:16:11','2014-12-26 20:16:11','',222,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/kimberly2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1555,7,'2014-12-26 12:16:12','2014-12-26 20:16:12','','kimberly3','','inherit','open','open','','kimberly3','','','2014-12-26 12:16:12','2014-12-26 20:16:12','',222,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/kimberly3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1557,7,'2014-12-26 12:39:16','2014-12-26 20:39:16','','tim1','','inherit','open','open','','tim1','','','2014-12-26 12:39:16','2014-12-26 20:39:16','',216,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/tim1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1558,7,'2014-12-26 12:39:17','2014-12-26 20:39:17','','tim2',''