 <strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Enrollment only with coach and dean approval; to confirm eligibility, please contact regina@improv.org.</p>\r\n<p>This advanced level four-week class is for advanced students who have improvised Shakespeare before.  You will  go deeper  and explore in-depth the devices, language, and characters of Shakespeare\'s plays, culminating in one performance on the Bayfront stage.  This workshop will allow you to play with a small ensemble of experienced people, familiarizing yourself with the nuances of the genre. We\'ll go beyond the first layer of Shakespearean language to what lies within the stories and tone of Shakespeare\'s plays to make them so timeless.  </p>','Performance - Advanced Shakes with Lisa (#15-02-2081)','','draft','open','open','','performance-advanced-shakes-with-lisa-15-02-2081','','','2015-02-23 16:34:40','2015-02-24 00:34:40','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=class&#038;p=1639',0,'class','',0),(1641,4,'2015-02-19 03:58:51','2015-02-19 11:58:51','','signature-email','','inherit','open','open','','signature-email','','','2015-02-19 03:58:51','2015-02-19 11:58:51','',0,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/signature-email.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1642,4,'2015-02-19 03:58:53','2015-02-19 11:58:53','','Email-logo-huffington','','inherit','open','open','','email-logo-huffington','','','2015-02-19 03:58:53','2015-02-19 11:58:53','',0,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Email-logo-huffington.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1643,5,'2015-02-19 15:46:13','2015-02-19 23:46:13','<h1>Sundays, 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM</h1>\r\n<p><strong>April 5, 2015 - May 10, 2015<br />Bayfront Theater, San Francisco<br /><br /></strong><strong>SOLD OUT! CLICK SIGN UP BUTTON TO GET ON THE WAIT LIST</strong><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Schedule</strong>: 6 sessions (once a week for 6 weeks)<br /> <strong>Class dates:</strong> April 5, 12, 19, 26, May 3, and 10<br /> <strong>Class length</strong>: 3 hours (18 hour