ong>Class length</strong>: 6 hours (18 hours total instruction)<br /> <strong>Tuition</strong>: $329<br /> <strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Enrollment only with coach and dean approval; to confirm eligibility, please contact regina@improv.org.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Want to explore the universe of Star Trek and perform it in a long form?  Then beam on over, this class is for you!  In this class you will learn how to improvise long form Star Trek (with more of a focus on the Original Series) and have one performance. We will cover many aspects of Star Trek - life on board a starship and in the universe of Star Trek, ranks and relationships including comfortably portraying the Captain all the way down to Crewman #2, alien planets, ship battles, mastering the science and technology while feeling calm and confident, all while learning long form and storytelling in a safe, supportive and fun environment.  In this class, we\'ll Boldly Go Where No One Has Gone Before! </span></p>','Performance - Star Trek with Laura (#15-04-2116)','','publish','open','open','','performance-star-trek-with-laura-15-04-2116','','','2015-03-04 12:19:48','2015-03-04 20:19:48','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=class&#038;p=1666',0,'class','',0),(1667,7,'2015-03-04 14:59:46','2015-03-04 22:59:46','','corey2','','inherit','open','open','','corey2','','','2015-03-04 14:59:46','2015-03-04 22:59:46','',228,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/corey2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1668,7,'2015-03-04 14:59:46','2015-03-04 22:59:46','','corey1','','inherit','open','open','','corey1','','','2015-03-04 14:59:46','2015-03-04 22:59:46','',228,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/corey1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1670,7,'2015-03-04 15:12:03','2015-03-04 23:12:03','','jenny3','','inherit','open','open','','jenny3','','','2015-03-04 15:12:03','2015-03-04 23:12:03','',226,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/jenny3.jpg',0,'attachment',