-content/uploads/2015/08/313-web-sf-noir1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2000,4,'2015-08-20 19:11:10','2015-08-21 02:11:10','','313-web-halloween-horror-musical','','inherit','closed','open','','313-web-halloween-horror-musical','','','2015-08-20 19:11:10','2015-08-21 02:11:10','',906,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/313-web-halloween-horror-musical.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2002,4,'2015-08-20 19:50:38','2015-08-21 02:50:38','<p>Every Super Scene show is jam-packed with genre!  Each night, we\'ll tell five different stories in five different genres.  You might see an musical right after a horror story, or a stage play right after an intergalactic space adventure.</p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"color: #d9541e;\"><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Group Tickets\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/groups/\"><strong>Group tickets</strong> start at just $14 each!</a><br /><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\">You can also give this show as a gift with a </a><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\"><strong>BATS Gift Certific</strong><strong>ate</strong>.</a> </span></em></p>','Super Scene','','publish','closed','open','','super-scene','','','2015-11-10 11:24:12','2015-11-10 19:24:12','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=friday&#038;p=2002',1,'friday','',0),(2005,4,'2015-08-20 20:55:43','2015-08-21 03:55:43','','313-web-superscene','','inherit','closed','open','','313-web-superscene','','','2015-08-20 20:55:43','2015-08-21 03:55:43','',2002,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/313-web-superscene.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2008,4,'2015-08-20 21:31:18','2015-08-21 04:31:18','<p>Secrets. Rivalries. Romance. Mistletoe!  These are the holiday episodes of Improvised Downton Abbey, which has become one of our most popular shows since it\'s debut in 2013.  You won\'t see Lady Mary, Lady Grantham, or Anna, instead our cast of world-class improvisers, inspired by your suggestions, will create all-new cast of characters on the spot (think of it as the estate down the road from Downton).  Each show will be set during the holiday season and will feature all-new characters and completely original storylines made-up on the spot. </p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"color: #d9541e;\"><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Group Tickets\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/groups/\"><strong>Group tickets</strong> start at just $14 each!</a><br /><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\">You can also give this show as a gift with a </a><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\"><strong>BATS Gift Certific</strong><strong>ate</strong>.</a> </span></em></p>','Improvised Downton Abbey','','publish','closed','open','','improvised-downton-abbey-2','','','2015-11-18 15:11:24','2015-11-18 23:11:24','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=special&#038;p=2008',2,'special','',0),(2009,4,'2015-08-20 21:48:48','2015-08-21 04:48:48','','313-web-downton-holiday','','inherit','closed','open','','313-web-downton-holiday','','','2015-08-20 21:48:48','2015-08-21 04:48:48','',2008,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/313-web-downton-holiday.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2010,4,'2015-08-20 21:57:00','2015-08-21 04:57:00','<p>This is the holiday voyage of a Starship to be named by you! Its mission: to explore new characters, seek out new dangerous and intense relationships, and to boldly go where no improv has gone before... all on the day after Christmas!</p>\r\n<p>Warp Speed is a completely improvised salute to that classic sci-fi TV series of the 60s. Instead seeing Kirk and Spock (or spoofs of Kirk and Spock), your suggestions will beam aboard an all-new crew of characters, created on the spot!</p>\r\n<p>Like every show at BATS, nothing will have been pre-planned or discussed in advance. There are no “stock characters” or pre-determined plot points or situations. Everything from the plot, to the dialogue, to the characters, to the music — and even the lighting cues — will be made up on the spot!</p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"color: #d9541e;\"><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Group Tickets\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/groups/\"><strong>Group tickets</strong> start at just $14 each!</a><br /><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\">You can also give this show as a gift with a </a><a style=\"color: #d9541e;\" title=\"Gift Certificates\" href=\"http://www.improv.org/shows/gift-certificates/\"><strong>BATS Gift Certific</strong><strong>ate</strong>.</a> </span></em></p>','Warp Speed<br><i>A Holiday Trek</i>','','publish','closed','open','','warp-speeda-holiday-trek','','','2015-09-19 21:36:23','2015-09-20 04:36:23','',0,'http://www.improv.org/?post_type=special&#038;p=2010',2,'special','',0),(2012,4,'2015-08-20 22:06:10','2015-08-21 05:06:10','','313-web-nye','','inherit','closed','open','','313-web-nye','','','2015-08-20 22:06:10','2015-08-21 05:06:10','',83,'http://www.improv.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/313-web-nye.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2013,4,'2015-08-20 22:24:29','2015-08-21 05:24:29','<p>Join us for \"The Best of BATS\" and ring in 2016 with a night of laughter.  Short scenes, songs, and games (and lots of audience participation) in the first half, followed by full-length story in the second half.  It\'s sure to be a magical evening that will capture your heart and imagination. Bring your friends, your family, or that special someone and enjoy a fun and unique start your New Year\'s Eve!  </p>\r\n<p>BATS NYE Special will begin promptly at 8:00 PM and will end before 10:00 PM, giving you plenty of time to make to make it your next destination before the ball drops.</p>\r\n<p><em><spa